    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy secret voice invites me still"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The sweetness of Thy yoke to prove;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And fain I would: but though my will"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Seems fixed, yet wide my passions rove;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet hindrances strew all the way;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I aim at Thee, yet from Thee stray."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Tis mercy all, that Thou hast brought"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My mind to seek her peace in Thee;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet, while I seek but find Thee not,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No peace my wand’ring soul shall see."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, when shall all my wand’rings end,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And all my steps to Thee-ward tend!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Is there a thing beneath the sun"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That strives with Thee my heart to share?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ah! tear it thence, and reign alone,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Lord of every motion there."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then shall my heart from earth be free,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When it has found repose in Thee."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, hide this self from me, that I"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No more, but Christ in me may live;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My vile affections mortify,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nor let one darling sin survive."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In all things nothing may I see,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nothing desire or seek but Thee."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O Lord, Thy sovereign aid impart,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To save me from low-thoughted care"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Chase this self-will through all my heart"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Through all its latent mazes there"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Make me Thy duteous child, that I"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ceaseless may Abba, Father, cry."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Each moment draw from earth away"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My heart which lowly waits Thy call;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Speak to my inmost soul and say"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“I am Thy Love, Thy God, Thy All.”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To feel Thy power, to hear Thy voice,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To taste Thy love, be all my choice."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    }
  ],
